@startuml
title Weather Station System State Diagram

[*] --> Shutdown

state Shutdown
state Running
state ConfigMode
state Prepared
state Controlled

Shutdown --> Running : restart
Shutdown --> ConfigMode : config required
Running --> ConfigMode : config required
Running --> Running : clock trigger
Running --> Prepared : data collection
Prepared --> Running : summary sent
Running --> Running : status check
ConfigMode --> Running : config completed
ConfigMode --> ConfigMode : config changes
Running --> Shutdown : shutdown command
ConfigMode --> Shutdown : shutdown command
Prepared --> Running : activity completed
Controlled --> Running : remote control

@enduml
